# victoria-metrics environment — copied to /etc/rustfs-mon/victoria-metrics.env
# Permissions: 0640 root:rustfs-mon
#
# All operational flags are baked into the unit file (ExecStart=...).
# This file is for optional add-ons only.

# ----- Optional HTTP basic auth -----
# If VM is reachable from outside the host (e.g., an OpenShift Grafana pod
# scraping it across the network), enable auth and add `-httpAuth.username`
# / `-httpAuth.password` flags via an override file or by editing the unit.
# Uncomment and set strong random values before exposing the port.
# VM_HTTP_AUTH_USER=monitoring
# VM_HTTP_AUTH_PASSWORD=CHANGE_ME_TO_RANDOM_STRING